<plot>An ancient talking macaw named Mac becomes the saving grace for an elderly man (Jason Robards) threatened with a nursing home, when it is discovered that the talking bird knows the whereabouts of a buried treasure from its days with a pirate. His grandson (Jamie Croft) decides to go off on the hunt only to discover that a resort now exists where the treasure is buried.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?585608</url></doc>
